{"id": 9, "category": "correctness", "description": "tool_choice forcing uses OpenAI-spec dict, but Ollama's OpenAI-compatible endpoint inconsistently honors function-named tool_choice. For models that ignore the directive, the strike loop never escapes — and even when honored, many Ollama tool-call implementations require the model to natively support function calling. With Qwen3-30B-Instruct (configured in .env) tool calling reliability is mixed; the loop will hit max_iterations=12 and fall back to `_fallback_answer` which just dumps raw rows formatted with str(), not a NL answer.", "reproducer": "text2sql/agent.py:93-99 (forced tool_choice) and agent.py:182-190 (fallback that prints raw column/row data instead of NL answer)", "code_ref": "text2sql/agent.py:93-99,182-190", "severity": "major", "demonstrability": "reasoned"}
{"id": 10, "category": "data_integrity", "description": "Date values converted via isoformat() string lose Oracle DATE time component semantics. For MONTH_DT (last day of month) Oracle returns DATETIME at 00:00:00; iso string '2025-12-31T00:00:00' is shown to the LLM. The LLM may compare these as strings or feed them back into SQL without DATE '...' wrapping, producing TO_DATE/ORA-01861 errors or wrong comparisons.", "reproducer": "text2sql/db.py:107-108 — `v.isoformat()` returns 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SS' string that no longer round-trips as Oracle DATE", "code_ref": "text2sql/db.py:107-108", "severity": "minor", "demonstrability": "reasoned"}
{"id": 11, "category": "semantics", "description": "Final-answer fallback dumps raw rows without units or formatting. When the LLM fails to call `final_answer`, `_fallback_answer` joins r.rows[:5] with str() — produces output like 'Результат запроса: колонки [TOTAL_INCOME], строки: 123456789' with no ₽ unit, no thousand separators, no business interpretation. Violates the spec's 'NL answer with numbers and interpretation' acceptance criterion.", "reproducer": "Spec requires '«1 234 567 890.12 ₽»' formatting; _fallback_answer outputs str(v) directly.", "code_ref": "text2sql/agent.py:182-190", "severity": "minor", "demonstrability": "reasoned"}
